reviews.text: Highly recommended! One of the best chinese marinated food  in Hong Kong! I love the marinated beef, tofu, pig ear and pig intestine. The taste is just right and no need extra sauce. Texture is very soft which proved that they know the very good secret of it. No matter what time i arrived (morning or afternoon, weekday or weekend), i have to queue up for at least 5-10mins. They serve take away only and no place to sit down.
